      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback and linear steering response expected of this chassis. Recent valve clearances have been shimmed to factory tolerances, ensuring the valvetrain remains quiet and efficient up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
